data.description: Welcome to your dream home in beautiful Summerville, SC! If you've been searching for a residence that combines the charm of a serene, private oasis with the convenience of a prime location, your search ends here.Nestled on a generous .69-acre lot, this property offers you the freedom you've longed for, with no HOA restrictions to hinder your vision. As you approach the home, you'll notice the thoughtful touches that set it apart. At the head of the driveway, a custom covered bench/bus stop invites you to pause and take in the beauty of the surroundings.For those who love to entertain, this home is primed and ready. An extended driveway and parking pad provide ample space for your guests, ensuring your gatherings are memorable and stress-free. Picture yourselfsipping sweet tea on the inviting front porch, where you can admire the front yard's lush greenery and the bounty of fruit trees.  Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the warmth of wood floors in the dining area and hallway. Molding and a tray ceiling add an elegant, custom touch to the space. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring pristine white cabinets and enough room for a kitchen table - the perfect spot for casual family meals. The eat-in area provides a picturesque view of the expansive backyard and the inviting inground pool.  On the main floor, two secondary bedrooms and a full bath round out the accommodations, offering comfort and convenience. Ascend to the second floor, and you'll discover a generously sized family room with tall ceilings and a cozy gas fireplace - the ideal place to unwind or entertain guests. An additional space adjacent to this room can be transformed into a cozy reading nook or a small bedroom. Storage options are abundant throughout the home, ensuring a clutter-free living space.  The master suite is a true retreat, boasting enough space to accommodate any furniture arrangement you desire. An exceptional feature of this home is HIS AND HERS bathrooms, eliminating any need to share counter space or personal space.  Now, let's talk about the pièce de résistance: the incredible 20' x 40' in-ground pool. The backyard is your private haven for outdoor parties and relaxation, with a spacious heat-resistant concrete deck that surrounds the pool. A charming pool house awaits, complete with guest quarters upstairs in the detached garage. This self-contained apartment offers a kitchenette, a full bathroom, a bedroom, and a living area - a perfect space for guests or potential rental income. Notably, the square footage of this apartment is not included in the main home's square footage.  If storage is a priority, you'll find an additional shed on the property, equipped with electricity to meet your storage needs.  This home epitomizes the Summerville lifestyle of your dreams, combining comfort, convenience, and freedom on a sprawling private lot. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own and experience the best of Summerville living.
